Umfazi uzakusungula igadango malungana nomyalo wokutlhala ngendlela ye-Faskh ekhotho efaneleko, bese ikambiso esebenza lapho izakuba yikambiso equntelwe ngeenkhathi ezithize mithetho yekhotho, kufaka nokusizakala okufaneleko, pendente lite, okutjhiwe kusigatjana 3f.
