Ngaphandle kokujamelana nanofana yini emumethwe kumThetho wokuLamula, 1965 mThetho 42 ka , nofana nanyana ngimuphi omunye umthetho, abalingani emtjhadweni wesiMuslimu bangavumelana ukuletha umbango ovuke ngesikhathi umtjhadwabo usesekhona nofana emtjhadweni onjalo kumlamuli kobana urarululwe ngokulamulwa.
