Lapha kubonakala kuqakatheke khulu khona, imitlolo ethize izakutjhugululelwa kinofana ngisiphi isibalo samanye amalimi alitjhumi asemthethweni bese asabalaliswe ngaphandle kokulindela isibawo esinjalo.
