Ukusetjenziswa kwelimi emisebenzini eqakatheke khulu efana neembhedlela zakarhulumende, iinteyitjhi zamapholisa, iindawo okurholelwa kizo, ama-ofisiwezindlu kanye nesiBethamthetho seGauteng kumele kusekelwe ngokukhutjhwa kwamaforomo wokusebenza okungenani ngelimi elingaphezu kwelilodwa lendabuko nofana nakunesidingo esikhulu kube ngamalimi wolitjhumi nanye asemthethweni.
